Our privacy notice provides an overview of how we process your personal data. “Personal data” refers to any information relating to you that we obtain from you or other parties.
GDPR
EU Regulation 2016/679
Nothing to worry about! It's simply for you to understand how we use your data! Our Bank complies with the new EU Regulation 2016/679 of the European Parliament and EU Council on the protection of physical persons with regard to the processing of personal data, which comes into force on the 25th of May 2018.
To whom it may concern
The Privacy Notice is ONLY directed to physical persons.
More information
If you require more information as to how we process and protect your personal data or you wish to learn more about the data protection, you may download the Privacy Notice below and our cookie policy
here
